  "texts": [
    "These include Adaptive Learning Platforms, which are educational systems that take into account the prior knowledge and performance of the workforce and customize the curriculum and tasks (Desaire, 2023).",
    "It is important to use the right tools and applications, which can be smartphones, tablets, and computers.",
    "Educational apps and platforms offer many interactive tools and content to help students learn.",
    "Nowadays, online teaching materials and courses are becoming more and more important.",
    "During the preparation, participants in the online training can progress at their own pace and choose relevant topics."
